PT J
AU Ruelos, VCB
   Masood, R
   Puzzitiello, RN
   Moverman, MA
   Pagani, NR
   Menendez, ME
   Salzler, MJ
AF Ruelos, Verdinand C. B.
   Masood, Raisa
